"Where do you mean...?"

What I most want to know is where I came from and why I'm here.

"...Well?"

When I shook my head, the man who had originally yelled at me grabbed me by the collar.


[Villager 1] "Huh?! What are you pretending to be?! You're trying to hog all the profits from selling off the elf for yourself, aren't you?!"


