Several years have passed since I arrived at the village after losing my memory.

According to the villagers, I've been living here since I was born.

However, one day he suddenly declared that he wanted to live a secluded life, disposed of his belongings, and moved into the forest.

At that time, an elf wandered into the village.

However, when I stole the elf from the village with the intention of selling him somewhere, I was instead captured by the other elves and had my memories stolen.

Even though they explained it to me, I have no memory of it so I can't feel any remorse or regret.

For the time being, he makes a living by cutting wood in the forest, which the villagers don't like to tread.

